WEBVTT

01:42.320 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

02:29.280 --> 02:30.760
Is the tutor not here yet?

02:31.880 --> 02:32.720
Or

02:33.760 --> 02:35.480
is he already in Sang Yan's room?

02:43.520 --> 02:44.480
He's not there.

02:50.600 --> 02:52.920
Sang Yan, I want some instant noodles.

02:53.440 --> 02:55.840
Add in two sausages and an egg!

02:56.960 --> 02:58.680
The tutor that Mom mentioned

02:58.760 --> 03:00.120
didn't come today, right?

03:00.880 --> 03:02.440
That means he's late.

03:03.000 --> 03:03.840
If that's the case,

03:03.920 --> 03:05.680
his professional conduct is problematic.

03:06.400 --> 03:08.120
You wouldn't be comfortable

03:08.200 --> 03:09.960
with someone like that tutoring me, right?

03:10.520 --> 03:11.440
So here's the deal.

03:12.240 --> 03:13.160
Sang Yan.

03:13.960 --> 03:15.960
How about you tell Mom

03:16.920 --> 03:18.880
not to get me a tutor

03:19.400 --> 03:21.680
during the New Year period?

03:21.760 --> 03:24.080
Tutors are hard to find
during this time anyway.

03:24.160 --> 03:25.760
Let's talk about it after New Year.

03:26.600 --> 03:27.440
Okay?

03:35.240 --> 03:37.080
If you're willing to speak for me,

03:37.160 --> 03:39.440
I'll give you 100 yuan this New Year.

03:44.560 --> 03:45.560
How about 200 yuan then?

03:47.920 --> 03:49.120
At most, five…

03:53.280 --> 03:55.480
What are you yelling for in the morning?

03:58.600 --> 03:59.880
That's Duan Jiaxu.

04:00.920 --> 04:01.880
Didn't Mom tell you?

04:01.960 --> 04:02.880
He's your tutor.

04:07.720 --> 04:08.560
Nonsense!

04:09.040 --> 04:10.880
How could you wake up so late?

04:10.960 --> 04:12.400
He has been waiting all morning!

04:12.480 --> 04:13.920
Lower your voice!

04:14.000 --> 04:14.960
Keep it down!

04:15.040 --> 04:16.480
Don't make me hit you!

04:19.040 --> 04:19.959
Breakfast is ready.

04:21.720 --> 04:22.600
Jiaxu.

04:22.680 --> 04:25.280
There aren't enough eggs.

04:25.360 --> 04:26.280
I'll add two more.

04:28.920 --> 04:29.960
Sang Zhi.

04:30.840 --> 04:32.160
Didn't you want instant noodles?

04:33.560 --> 04:35.000
Two sausages and one egg.

04:38.840 --> 04:40.520
Eat up. The noodles will get lumpy soon.

04:41.760 --> 04:42.640
Got it.

04:47.280 --> 04:49.760
An egg and two ham sausages.

05:13.000 --> 05:14.560
You were sleeping so soundly just now.

05:15.200 --> 05:17.040
Your brother couldn't even wake you up.

05:18.960 --> 05:20.400
I stayed up too late last night

05:20.480 --> 05:21.360
working on homework.

05:22.040 --> 05:23.040
Is that so?

05:23.120 --> 05:24.800
I thought you pretended not to hear him.

05:25.320 --> 05:27.760
No, I really didn't hear him.

05:29.240 --> 05:30.080
Next time…

05:31.160 --> 05:32.720
I'll set off firecrackers at your door!

05:34.680 --> 05:35.560
Here.

05:37.840 --> 05:38.960
Thank you, Jiaxu.

05:50.280 --> 05:51.600
Is it tasty?

05:53.200 --> 05:54.080
Yes.

05:55.520 --> 05:56.680
Here.

05:56.760 --> 05:57.760
Have some more.

06:32.440 --> 06:35.080
Have you been secretly practicing at home?

06:35.160 --> 06:36.520
Do I even need to do that?

06:36.600 --> 06:38.680
SOCCER FIELD

06:48.880 --> 06:49.720
Sang Zhi.

07:00.880 --> 07:02.200
Get out of the way!

07:03.880 --> 07:05.400
Don't I have a tutoring session?

07:06.120 --> 07:07.760
But we just finished breakfast!

07:07.840 --> 07:09.520
Do your own reading first.

07:09.600 --> 07:11.520
Am I the one getting tutored or are you?

07:13.200 --> 07:14.400
Sang Zhi.

07:14.480 --> 07:15.560
Go and take a rest first.

07:15.640 --> 07:16.760
I'll come and tutor you

07:16.840 --> 07:17.880
after this game, all right?

07:17.960 --> 07:18.880
Sure.

07:24.840 --> 07:27.080
Jiaxu, do you want some fruit?

07:27.160 --> 07:28.040
No.

07:30.520 --> 07:33.120
Just say so if you want some.

07:33.200 --> 07:35.200
I'll cut it for you. Why all the hassle?

07:35.280 --> 07:37.120
Don't be so mean to her all the time.

07:39.600 --> 07:40.600
How do we beat this level?

07:40.680 --> 07:41.560
Go to the left first.

07:42.520 --> 07:43.440
Help me with this.

07:44.800 --> 07:46.560
This is such a huge watermelon.

07:46.640 --> 07:48.960
You won't be able to cut it using this.

07:49.040 --> 07:50.080
It will work.

07:51.120 --> 07:53.040
You can't cut it with this.

07:53.120 --> 07:54.480
I've only been playing for a while.

07:54.560 --> 07:55.520
Now I have to serve you.

07:55.600 --> 07:56.440
I'm not cutting it!

07:56.520 --> 07:58.040
- Sang Zhi.
- I won't do it!

07:58.120 --> 07:59.200
Take a look at this first.

07:59.280 --> 08:01.440
I'll cut the watermelon after this game.

08:04.440 --> 08:06.000
I thought you'd question my credentials.

08:06.080 --> 08:07.440
After accepting this resume,

08:07.920 --> 08:09.720
you're not allowed to replace me, okay?

08:09.800 --> 08:11.280
Don't worry.

08:11.800 --> 08:13.440
No one is willing to tutor her except you.

08:13.520 --> 08:15.680
She has no other option but you.

08:17.760 --> 08:19.040
"Duan Jiaxu."

08:19.640 --> 08:21.280
So this is how you spell it.

08:22.200 --> 08:24.200
Why didn't he attach his photo?

08:24.280 --> 08:25.280
That's wrong.

08:25.360 --> 08:26.840
Do we go to the right first?

08:26.920 --> 08:27.960
Jump!

08:28.800 --> 08:29.680
Awesome!

08:34.320 --> 08:35.840
Okay, go up.

08:39.440 --> 08:40.320
Isn't it upper right?

08:44.120 --> 08:45.880
Should we go right or…

08:51.160 --> 08:52.160
Lower right.

08:53.160 --> 08:54.320
That's not it either.

09:01.080 --> 09:02.840
Try upper left. Try it.

09:03.800 --> 09:04.880
Go up?

09:04.960 --> 09:05.800
Upper left.

09:08.280 --> 09:09.120
We did it!

09:29.760 --> 09:30.840
What were you photographing?

09:33.520 --> 09:34.440
Me?

09:35.320 --> 09:36.360
Him?

09:37.160 --> 09:38.320
Why would you take his photo?

09:39.680 --> 09:41.120
Is he as handsome as me?

09:46.520 --> 09:48.200
Are you planning to show Mom and Dad

09:48.280 --> 09:49.920
- that we're gaming?
- I…

09:52.320 --> 09:53.400
I'm not.

09:57.760 --> 09:58.680
I just have a classmate

09:58.760 --> 10:00.560
who said my brother is very handsome.

10:00.640 --> 10:02.040
I can't show her a photo of you.

10:02.640 --> 10:04.360
- It would be humiliating for me.
- Hey!

10:04.440 --> 10:05.920
I would prefer you rat us out!

10:06.000 --> 10:06.920
Come back here!

10:08.400 --> 10:09.240
Attention!

10:10.200 --> 10:11.640
At ease!

10:15.400 --> 10:16.920
She's simply impossible.

10:17.720 --> 10:18.920
Try to understand her.

10:19.000 --> 10:20.800
Kids her age

10:20.880 --> 10:22.240
naturally have some sense of pride.

10:24.000 --> 10:25.440
That's nonsense!

10:25.520 --> 10:26.640
It's all your fault!

10:27.400 --> 10:29.000
Come on. Let's continue.

10:52.040 --> 10:53.160
CONTACT SETTINGS

10:53.240 --> 10:55.160
NOTES AND TAGS SETTINGS

10:55.240 --> 10:58.640
DUAN XX

11:02.800 --> 11:05.120
CHAPTER FIVE, SECRETLY

11:05.200 --> 11:07.520
THE NAME ENGRAVED IN MY HEART

11:08.280 --> 11:12.360
NOTES AND LABELS SETTINGS

11:12.440 --> 11:16.600
NOTES AND LABELS SETTINGS

11:20.360 --> 11:25.920
JIAXU

11:26.000 --> 11:28.320
SAVING

11:28.400 --> 11:30.600
JIAXU

11:45.640 --> 11:46.720
Sang Zhi.

11:51.040 --> 11:52.600
I've cut the watermelon for you.

11:59.760 --> 12:00.920
Show me.

12:05.400 --> 12:06.760
The photo you took just now.

12:10.520 --> 12:11.600
What's wrong?

12:11.680 --> 12:13.600
I want to check if it's ugly or not.

12:13.680 --> 12:15.000
If so, you can snap a few more.

12:16.040 --> 12:17.200
Didn't you say

12:17.280 --> 12:20.080
that you want to show your classmate
a handsome brother?

12:20.160 --> 12:21.440
I can't make you look bad.

12:24.000 --> 12:25.760
Don't we have a tutoring session?

12:25.840 --> 12:26.800
Let's get on with it.

12:30.040 --> 12:32.320
I'm eager to learn today.

12:33.640 --> 12:35.440
And now you love learning?

12:37.920 --> 12:39.760
Come, show me

12:40.680 --> 12:42.880
your last physics final exam.

12:58.320 --> 12:59.840
Did you not pay attention in class?

12:59.920 --> 13:01.480
How could you get this question wrong?

13:04.480 --> 13:05.400
I did pay attention.

13:05.480 --> 13:06.600
I just didn't understand it.

13:08.440 --> 13:10.560
This question on conservation of energy
was a giveaway.

13:11.680 --> 13:13.040
At first…

13:13.120 --> 13:16.760
At first, I wanted to choose B.

13:17.240 --> 13:18.160
That's right.

13:19.160 --> 13:20.640
The correct answer is A.

13:27.160 --> 13:28.480
Remember it.

13:28.560 --> 13:31.120
Don't get problems
on conservation of energy wrong again.

13:32.680 --> 13:34.520
Maybe I didn't pay enough attention.

13:35.240 --> 13:36.800
But even if I had paid full attention,

13:36.880 --> 13:38.080
I wouldn't have understood it.

13:38.640 --> 13:39.640
This is really difficult.

13:41.000 --> 13:42.560
Didn't I tell you last time

13:42.640 --> 13:43.720
to pay attention in class?

13:43.800 --> 13:44.640
Have you forgotten?

13:45.640 --> 13:47.240
That was such a long time ago.

13:47.320 --> 13:48.560
Are you saying

13:48.640 --> 13:50.240
that I need to remind you every day?

13:53.040 --> 13:53.920
Can you?

13:57.720 --> 13:59.000
Give me your physics book.

14:01.880 --> 14:03.800
I'll start off with Ampère's Law.

14:05.680 --> 14:07.240
Do you know the Left-Hand Rule?

14:10.040 --> 14:10.920
Look.

14:11.680 --> 14:14.080
Let's say
there is a uniform magnetic field.

14:14.160 --> 14:15.960
This is the direction of the current.

14:16.040 --> 14:17.360
Now hold out your left hand.

14:47.760 --> 14:49.080
Digest this first.

14:50.400 --> 14:52.280
Work on this practice test.

14:52.360 --> 14:53.240
I'll check it later.

14:57.040 --> 14:58.480
I'll give you three lessons a week

14:58.560 --> 15:00.160
during the winter break.

15:05.800 --> 15:07.080
Is that too much for you?

15:07.800 --> 15:08.720
No.

15:10.120 --> 15:11.280
That's too little.

15:12.360 --> 15:14.000
Can we have lessons every day?

15:15.040 --> 15:16.800
I have my internship four days a week.

15:16.880 --> 15:18.480
The remaining three days are all yours.

15:24.160 --> 15:27.360
I thought you didn't want a tutor.

15:31.000 --> 15:32.520
You're pretty good at teaching.

15:33.400 --> 15:34.640
It's novel.

15:36.520 --> 15:37.520
Of course.

15:39.480 --> 15:41.120
You're unexpectedly eager to learn now.

15:41.200 --> 15:42.120
Not bad.

15:45.600 --> 15:46.600
Focus!

15:48.800 --> 15:49.880
Next time,

15:49.960 --> 15:51.640
I can explain

15:52.400 --> 15:53.520
the Lorentz force to you.

15:56.640 --> 15:58.000
By the way, Jiaxu.

15:59.800 --> 16:01.160
Can I ask you a question?

16:01.240 --> 16:02.280
Go ahead.

16:05.240 --> 16:07.520
Why did you choose a university in Nanwu

16:07.600 --> 16:09.040
instead of Yihe?

16:09.920 --> 16:11.160
Isn't Yihe University also good?

16:13.640 --> 16:16.840
I didn't want to stay in Yihe.

16:16.920 --> 16:19.360
Isn't it nice to explore other places?

16:19.440 --> 16:21.000
Why did you choose Nanwu then?

16:25.360 --> 16:26.720
How do I put this?

16:28.520 --> 16:29.720
My dream

16:29.800 --> 16:31.800
is to eventually work
in the gaming industry.

16:32.440 --> 16:33.640
Nanwu is the city

16:33.720 --> 16:35.760
with the biggest gaming industry.

16:35.840 --> 16:36.920
That's why I came here.

16:39.280 --> 16:40.440
What are you thinking about?

16:42.160 --> 16:43.240
Hurry up and do your work.

17:18.760 --> 17:19.880
Sorry, I'm late.

17:22.119 --> 17:24.319
So have you digested what I taught you

17:24.400 --> 17:25.440
in the last lesson?

17:27.599 --> 17:30.240
Jiaxu, did you not sleep?

17:31.560 --> 17:33.040
I was working late yesterday,

17:33.120 --> 17:34.000
so I slept late.

17:35.360 --> 17:36.280
Let's see.

17:39.000 --> 17:41.600
Why don't I do my homework first?

17:42.080 --> 17:43.880
You can check it after I'm done

17:43.960 --> 17:45.480
and explain anything that is incorrect.

17:45.560 --> 17:48.240
You have nothing to do
while I work on it anyway,

17:48.320 --> 17:50.000
so you can go and rest for a while.

17:50.720 --> 17:51.880
What do you mean?

17:51.960 --> 17:53.040
Are you trying to slack off?

17:53.120 --> 17:54.920
Or will you tell on me to your parents

17:55.000 --> 17:56.240
so that they can replace me?

17:56.320 --> 17:57.320
That's not it.

17:59.840 --> 18:01.560
I was just kidding. How about this?

18:01.640 --> 18:03.240
You can

18:05.320 --> 18:06.800
complete this set of problems.

18:09.160 --> 18:11.480
I'll go over it with you when you're done.

18:11.560 --> 18:12.520
Wake me up later.

18:13.440 --> 18:14.480
I'm going to take a nap.

19:28.800 --> 19:29.640
Are you slacking off?

19:41.080 --> 19:41.920
What were you up to?

19:43.680 --> 19:44.920
Slacking off.

19:45.640 --> 19:46.720
Have you done the problems?

19:53.640 --> 19:54.760
Show me

19:56.280 --> 19:58.680
the set of problems you worked on
over the weekend.

20:16.200 --> 20:17.600
This problem.

20:19.080 --> 20:20.280
You got it wrong.

20:20.360 --> 20:21.960
The electric charge is negative.

20:22.040 --> 20:23.240
So its direction of motion

20:23.320 --> 20:25.040
is opposite to that of the current.

20:29.800 --> 20:31.600
I guess I'm bad at tutoring.

20:31.680 --> 20:32.720
You're getting worse.

20:34.880 --> 20:35.720
Jiaxu.

20:36.880 --> 20:38.480
Be more confident.

20:38.560 --> 20:39.760
You've tutored me well.

20:39.840 --> 20:42.600
I just can't remember very well

20:42.680 --> 20:44.280
and I really don't understand it.

20:44.360 --> 20:46.400
I just don't find physics interesting,

20:46.480 --> 20:48.840
so it's hard for me to remember things.

20:48.920 --> 20:50.280
What do you find interesting then?

20:57.800 --> 20:59.720
In short, physics is boring.

21:13.680 --> 21:15.000
I work so hard to tutor every day,

21:15.080 --> 21:16.240
but you have a leisurely time.

21:16.320 --> 21:18.360
Yes, it's your tutoring session, not mine!

21:19.000 --> 21:20.080
Let me play a few rounds.

21:21.480 --> 21:22.760
My legs!

21:22.840 --> 21:23.880
Go away!

21:23.960 --> 21:24.960
Get off!

21:26.800 --> 21:28.360
Come on. Let's play together.

21:28.440 --> 21:29.840
Airdrops! Go that way.

21:31.160 --> 21:33.080
- I have something to tell you.
- What is it?

21:33.160 --> 21:34.480
Don't tell me you're quitting!

21:35.600 --> 21:36.960
Don't be ridiculous.

21:37.040 --> 21:38.480
I'm so good at tutoring.

21:39.640 --> 21:41.600
I wanted to say
that I want to take the kiddo

21:41.680 --> 21:44.320
to the Science and Technology Museum
in the city when we're all free.

21:44.400 --> 21:45.720
Why?

21:45.800 --> 21:47.640
She currently has no interest in physics

21:47.720 --> 21:48.680
and can't learn.

21:49.400 --> 21:51.680
So I thought
that maybe a visit to the museum

21:51.760 --> 21:53.960
might be able to pique her interest.

21:54.680 --> 21:56.480
You're pretty responsible.

21:56.560 --> 21:57.520
If I didn't know better,

21:57.600 --> 21:59.120
I would think you were her brother.

21:59.200 --> 22:00.840
Please also tell your parents for me.

22:02.000 --> 22:02.960
No need.

22:03.040 --> 22:04.680
They're very busy at the end of the year.

22:04.760 --> 22:06.320
As her backup brother, I can decide.

22:07.880 --> 22:09.280
When are we going?

22:09.360 --> 22:10.560
I'll tell you when it's time.

22:10.640 --> 22:13.320
- Hurry up! We're driving.
- There's nobody around. Don't worry.

22:21.760 --> 22:23.040
Have you been here before?

22:23.840 --> 22:25.040
No.

22:26.080 --> 22:27.400
This place is quite interesting.

22:27.480 --> 22:29.240
I used to love coming here.

22:32.400 --> 22:33.240
Only two tickets?

22:33.320 --> 22:34.160
Are you not going in?

22:34.240 --> 22:36.920
Only brats would visit a science museum.

22:37.000 --> 22:38.200
Of course I'm not interested.

22:38.280 --> 22:39.520
Who's the brat now?

22:41.880 --> 22:43.080
That's enough.

22:43.840 --> 22:46.040
I gave you money for three tickets.

22:46.120 --> 22:47.400
Give me back my change.

22:48.160 --> 22:49.840
I'll use it on games at the cybercafe.

22:49.920 --> 22:51.560
I'll pick you guys up later. Bye!

22:54.560 --> 22:55.920
How pretentious!

22:56.000 --> 22:56.880
Let's go.

22:56.960 --> 22:58.160
I'll show you around inside.

23:08.000 --> 23:09.880
Don't you think this slide is interesting?

23:11.360 --> 23:13.320
There are a lot of physics concepts to it.

23:14.040 --> 23:16.920
The reason that this slide is curved

23:17.000 --> 23:18.560
instead of being a straight line

23:18.640 --> 23:21.280
is based on
the brachistochrone curve principle.

23:21.360 --> 23:23.240
Therefore, although this slide looks high,

23:23.320 --> 23:24.320
when you slide down,

23:24.400 --> 23:25.920
you'll go fast in the middle portion,

23:26.000 --> 23:28.360
then slow down toward the end.

23:28.440 --> 23:30.200
That also makes it safer.

23:31.160 --> 23:32.440
Do you want to try it out?

23:33.280 --> 23:34.360
Go and have some fun.

23:37.480 --> 23:38.320
Let's go!

23:46.960 --> 23:47.880
How was it?

23:47.960 --> 23:48.920
Was it fun?

23:50.720 --> 23:52.960
Wasn't the middle section
particularly exciting?

23:53.040 --> 23:55.360
Yes, but it wasn't that fast.

23:55.440 --> 23:57.360
That's the physics principle

23:57.440 --> 23:58.560
that I just told you about.

24:03.440 --> 24:05.760
Here's a bonus geographical fact for you.

24:06.680 --> 24:07.640
The tsunami.

24:07.720 --> 24:09.960
Did you know
that the definition of a tsunami

24:10.040 --> 24:12.000
is a catastrophic wave,

24:12.080 --> 24:14.560
usually caused
by an underwater earthquake?

24:15.520 --> 24:17.720
It can reach a maximum wave speed

24:17.800 --> 24:19.320
of over 700 km per hour.

24:19.880 --> 24:21.680
Also, look at the waves.

24:22.160 --> 24:24.760
They may be only 1 m high in the sea,

24:24.840 --> 24:26.160
but when they reach the shore,

24:26.240 --> 24:27.560
they can be tens of meters high.

24:27.640 --> 24:29.000
Hence, it's a huge threat

24:29.080 --> 24:30.280
to cities by the sea.

24:31.160 --> 24:32.320
What?

24:32.400 --> 24:33.320
Run!

24:36.840 --> 24:37.920
Hurry up, Jiaxu!

24:38.000 --> 24:39.720
The tsunami is going to drown us!

24:39.800 --> 24:40.800
How is that possible?

24:40.880 --> 24:42.560
We've outrun the tsunami.

24:46.120 --> 24:47.080
Come and try this out.

24:49.320 --> 24:50.400
Put both your hands

24:50.480 --> 24:52.240
on top of this flowerpot.

24:55.400 --> 24:56.280
Look at the screen.

25:03.240 --> 25:04.360
This is incredible!

25:04.440 --> 25:06.200
This is thermoelectric sensing technology.

25:06.880 --> 25:09.040
When the flowerpot senses
your palm's temperature,

25:09.120 --> 25:11.000
its thermoelectric sensor

25:11.080 --> 25:12.960
will convert the change in temperature

25:13.040 --> 25:14.680
into a change in power,

25:14.760 --> 25:16.600
which triggers this animation.

25:17.520 --> 25:18.720
- Look.
- That's so cool.

25:18.800 --> 25:20.680
The blooming flowers
are attracting butterflies.

25:20.760 --> 25:22.360
It's actually related to physics as well.

25:23.400 --> 25:24.440
How amazing!

25:30.120 --> 25:32.040
Here's my suggestion, Sang Zhi.

25:32.680 --> 25:33.520
I know

25:33.600 --> 25:36.120
you may have your personal preferences,

25:36.200 --> 25:38.400
but try not to get sidetracked

25:38.480 --> 25:39.760
and study hard.

25:40.320 --> 25:41.800
It's because your future dreams

25:41.880 --> 25:43.520
and the things
you want to do in the future

25:43.600 --> 25:46.080
will probably need to be achieved
through studying.

25:50.640 --> 25:51.800
Jiaxu.

25:51.880 --> 25:53.840
I think you were probably very rebellious

25:53.920 --> 25:55.080
when you were my age.

25:55.160 --> 25:56.200
Why?

25:56.280 --> 25:57.400
Because you play video games.

25:57.480 --> 25:59.520
Does that make me rebellious?

25:59.600 --> 26:01.400
My teacher said
that we can't play video games.

26:03.040 --> 26:05.320
When I was your age,

26:05.400 --> 26:08.320
I would be overjoyed
if I could play video games

26:08.400 --> 26:09.680
for just one hour a week.

26:11.680 --> 26:12.920
Those were the moments

26:15.320 --> 26:16.760
when I could escape

26:16.840 --> 26:18.520
from the negative realities of my life

26:18.600 --> 26:19.800
by playing video games

26:19.880 --> 26:20.880
and get a break.

26:30.880 --> 26:31.840
Well,

26:33.160 --> 26:34.680
I guess games

26:36.280 --> 26:37.600
aren't that bad.

26:39.720 --> 26:41.600
So,

26:42.080 --> 26:44.080
you think video games can bring you

26:44.160 --> 26:46.160
joy and comfort, right?

26:46.240 --> 26:47.120
That's right.

26:47.680 --> 26:50.440
Don't you find it very relaxing
to play video games?

26:51.360 --> 26:53.280
So at that time,

26:53.360 --> 26:56.560
I dreamed of creating my own video game

26:56.640 --> 26:59.360
and spreading joy to more people.

27:08.760 --> 27:10.120
I'll study hard

27:11.920 --> 27:14.120
and find my own dream.

27:15.720 --> 27:17.520
But you have to work hard too, Jiaxu.

27:18.080 --> 27:19.680
Because I think

27:22.080 --> 27:24.560
you'll be able to achieve your dream soon.

27:26.400 --> 27:27.760
Do you have such faith in me?

27:29.480 --> 27:31.880
Let's work hard together then.

27:31.960 --> 27:33.120
We can do it.

27:34.640 --> 27:35.560
Okay!

28:02.240 --> 28:03.120
Have some water.

28:10.840 --> 28:13.280
I noticed you like to draw.

28:15.160 --> 28:17.680
Drawing is a hobby that you can keep up.

28:18.160 --> 28:20.680
It takes imagination to draw.

28:21.400 --> 28:22.240
Besides,

28:23.080 --> 28:25.200
I've always felt
that people who like to draw

28:25.280 --> 28:27.240
are full of kindness to the world.

28:27.320 --> 28:30.120
They can record
what they find beautiful in this world

28:30.200 --> 28:31.560
through their paintbrush.

28:31.640 --> 28:32.520
Jiaxu.

28:35.120 --> 28:36.360
Can you not

28:38.440 --> 28:39.600
be in a relationship?

28:47.160 --> 28:48.120
What do you mean?

28:50.000 --> 28:51.840
Don't you have a dream too?

28:52.800 --> 28:54.080
If you get into a relationship,

28:54.160 --> 28:56.240
you'll delay your dream.

28:58.080 --> 28:59.920
I'm almost done with university.

29:00.000 --> 29:01.720
Do I still need to avoid dating

29:01.800 --> 29:03.120
for the sake of my studies?

29:03.800 --> 29:05.560
Why don't you say this to your brother?

29:05.640 --> 29:06.480
I…

29:09.880 --> 29:11.240
I did.

29:11.320 --> 29:12.440
What did he say?

29:13.160 --> 29:14.880
He said, "Go away, little demon!"

29:17.160 --> 29:18.520
I'm saying this

29:18.600 --> 29:20.400
because my classmate's brother

29:20.480 --> 29:21.840
had a girlfriend.

29:22.760 --> 29:25.440
But that girl treated
my classmate really badly.

29:25.920 --> 29:27.120
How so?

29:27.640 --> 29:28.600
I don't know.

29:29.160 --> 29:30.720
She treated your classmate badly?

29:32.160 --> 29:33.400
Moreover,

29:33.480 --> 29:35.360
if you have a girlfriend,

29:36.640 --> 29:38.840
you won't be able to be so nice to me.

29:40.920 --> 29:42.560
Now you realize that I'm nice to you.

29:44.480 --> 29:46.440
Why are you thinking that far ahead?

29:46.520 --> 29:48.320
If you don't see me for a couple of years,

29:48.400 --> 29:49.800
you might forget all about me.

29:53.840 --> 29:54.680
How about this then?

29:55.520 --> 29:56.760
In the future,

29:56.840 --> 29:58.920
I'll find a gentle girlfriend

29:59.000 --> 30:00.480
who treats you well.

30:01.120 --> 30:02.680
This way, you will have

30:02.760 --> 30:04.680
one more person who is good to you.

30:04.760 --> 30:05.600
All right?

30:16.320 --> 30:17.240
Fine.

30:19.040 --> 30:20.920
When you find one,

30:23.000 --> 30:25.800
can you show her to me first?

30:27.000 --> 30:28.240
Sure.

30:28.320 --> 30:30.440
I'll show you when I find one.

30:33.480 --> 30:34.320
I'll remember that.

30:44.840 --> 30:46.400
Is there anything else you want to see?

30:47.320 --> 30:48.200
Your brother is here.

30:48.280 --> 30:50.040
Let's call it a day if you're tired.

30:51.040 --> 30:51.960
Let's go.

30:55.640 --> 30:56.600
Sang Yan!

30:58.000 --> 31:00.000
- Hey.
- What's wrong with you?

31:01.760 --> 31:02.640
How was it?

31:03.160 --> 31:04.600
Did you find the motivation to study?

31:07.800 --> 31:08.920
Yes.

31:09.600 --> 31:10.440
Well?

31:10.520 --> 31:13.080
We went on a slide

31:13.160 --> 31:14.680
and we went down like this.

31:14.760 --> 31:16.440
- Weren't you there to learn?
- Hello, Li Xun?

31:16.520 --> 31:18.200
- It also lit up.
- I've modified that.

31:18.280 --> 31:20.400
- I sent it to you this morning.
- And there was water.

31:20.480 --> 31:22.840
- A water screen.
- Does it need more revisions?

31:22.920 --> 31:25.520
- Were you just playing around?
- Okay, I have my laptop with me.

31:25.600 --> 31:27.800
I'll find a place to do the revisions
and send it to you.

31:27.880 --> 31:29.600
- Okay, bye.
- I'm only telling you what I saw.

31:31.720 --> 31:33.160
Take your sister home first.

31:33.240 --> 31:34.960
I'm going to do some work over there.

31:35.440 --> 31:36.400
Okay.

31:37.600 --> 31:39.000
Remember what I told you today.

31:40.400 --> 31:41.920
- Go home.
- Do you need a ride?

31:42.000 --> 31:42.880
No, thank you.

31:49.200 --> 31:50.680
Here, put on your ugly hat.

31:54.360 --> 31:55.200
Where's the strap?

31:56.480 --> 31:57.760
Go away!

32:02.080 --> 32:04.200
Stupid little demon, I'm so nice to you

32:04.280 --> 32:05.600
and you didn't even wait for me.

32:15.320 --> 32:16.520
Sang Yan!

32:18.680 --> 32:20.120
My sketchbook is missing.

32:20.200 --> 32:21.920
It's that book that I usually draw in.

32:22.480 --> 32:24.280
There was nothing in the car just now.

32:24.360 --> 32:26.480
Are you sure? Take me there and show me.

32:26.560 --> 32:27.400
Let's go!

32:27.480 --> 32:28.840
There's really nothing there.

32:29.400 --> 32:30.400
I've told you.

32:30.480 --> 32:32.240
Just buy another one if you've lost it.

32:33.440 --> 32:35.200
Are you sure you've checked everywhere?

32:35.280 --> 32:36.440
Yes!

32:40.360 --> 32:42.000
From the Science and Technology Museum

32:43.280 --> 32:44.440
to here.

32:44.520 --> 32:45.440
The car.

32:46.160 --> 32:47.080
My room.

33:00.440 --> 33:01.600
The museum.

33:13.520 --> 33:14.720
Hello.

33:14.800 --> 33:17.160
I visited
the Science and Technology Museum today

33:17.240 --> 33:19.560
and accidentally left my sketchbook there.

33:19.640 --> 33:21.080
It's a green sketchbook.

33:21.160 --> 33:22.600
Did you pick it up?

33:22.680 --> 33:23.800
Yes.

33:27.480 --> 33:30.040
We passed it to the boy who was with you.

33:30.120 --> 33:31.320
Did he not give it to you?

33:36.760 --> 33:39.240
PURE MILK

33:39.320 --> 33:41.480
SLEEPY

33:49.600 --> 33:52.840
What should I do if Jiaxu sees it?

34:06.000 --> 34:07.920
Little demon, I have your sketchbook.

34:09.000 --> 34:11.280
- I'm tossing it if you don't want it.
- Give it to me!

34:13.679 --> 34:14.880
Duan Jiaxu dropped it off

34:14.960 --> 34:16.000
on his way to work.

34:17.360 --> 34:18.320
Did he look inside?

34:19.000 --> 34:20.719
How would I know?

34:20.800 --> 34:22.239
Why didn't you ask him?

34:23.600 --> 34:25.679
Is there anything shady in there?

34:25.760 --> 34:26.800
No.

34:26.880 --> 34:29.120
Fine. I'm going back to sleep.

34:45.840 --> 34:48.000
He could've just called me.

34:48.840 --> 34:50.880
Why did he ask Sang Yan to pass it to me?

34:52.199 --> 34:55.880
Doesn't that mean he has looked inside

34:56.880 --> 34:58.160
and felt awkward?

34:58.640 --> 35:00.560
That's why
he didn't give it to me himself!

35:07.440 --> 35:11.560
Then what if…

35:28.720 --> 35:29.800
Why are you back?

35:31.600 --> 35:33.720
I can't stand it at home.

35:34.480 --> 35:36.200
Did you come back to keep me company?

35:36.280 --> 35:37.920
By the way, Jiaxu, listen.

35:38.600 --> 35:39.600
Don't come on Tuesday.

35:39.680 --> 35:40.680
Come on Thursday instead.

35:40.760 --> 35:41.640
Why?

35:41.720 --> 35:43.040
The little demon has puppy love.

35:43.600 --> 35:45.880
I gave her an earful
and confiscated her phone and laptop.

35:45.960 --> 35:47.480
She won't be in the mood to study,

35:47.560 --> 35:48.400
so forget it.

35:48.480 --> 35:49.400
Puppy love?

35:51.000 --> 35:52.440
Is it with that classmate of hers?

35:53.360 --> 35:55.320
No, it's online dating!
Can you believe it?

35:55.400 --> 35:57.000
What?

35:57.080 --> 35:58.880
That's right. She told me herself.

35:58.960 --> 36:01.200
All right, I'll come next week then.

36:04.240 --> 36:06.080
It's normal for her to experience this

36:06.160 --> 36:07.160
at her age.

36:07.720 --> 36:09.160
Anyway, just talk some sense into her

36:09.240 --> 36:10.880
and make sure she knows the limits.

36:10.960 --> 36:12.480
I'm sure she will get it.

36:13.000 --> 36:14.200
Guess what?

36:14.280 --> 36:15.720
I don't care about other people.

36:16.400 --> 36:18.360
But it's not allowed for my sister!

36:18.440 --> 36:20.160
They must break up

36:20.240 --> 36:22.000
or I'll beat that guy up!

37:03.240 --> 37:05.320
He should alreadyknow

37:05.400 --> 37:08.240
about the online dating story
that I made up.

37:10.000 --> 37:11.240
How should I face him

37:11.840 --> 37:13.880
during our lesson later?

37:14.480 --> 37:16.360
He will no longer think

37:16.440 --> 37:18.360
that I drew him, right?

37:18.440 --> 37:21.720
How should a heartbroken person look like?

37:23.000 --> 37:24.680
Should I act sad,

37:24.760 --> 37:26.160
upset, and miserable?

37:29.320 --> 37:31.000
Will he not believe it?

37:31.760 --> 37:33.040
- Or should I--
- Little demon!

37:34.280 --> 37:35.280
Little demon!

37:37.400 --> 37:38.640
Little demon.

37:50.200 --> 37:51.120
How have you been

37:52.080 --> 37:53.400
these past few days?

38:02.440 --> 38:04.360
I'll take you for a ride

38:04.440 --> 38:05.640
when you finish your lesson.

38:10.480 --> 38:12.120
I won't tell Mom and Dad.

38:12.200 --> 38:13.560
I don't want to be scolded either.

38:39.000 --> 38:40.120
I heard from your brother

38:40.880 --> 38:42.360
that you're dating online.

38:45.400 --> 38:46.600
How did you meet him?

38:46.680 --> 38:47.640
Tell me.

38:50.560 --> 38:52.400
You don't have to be so nosy.

38:52.880 --> 38:54.640
What's wrong with caring about you?

38:56.720 --> 38:58.400
You asked me not to date,

38:58.480 --> 38:59.840
but you did it yourself.

39:01.240 --> 39:02.880
From what he said,

39:02.960 --> 39:05.320
he likely believes that the one I like

39:05.400 --> 39:07.680
is the non-existent online friend.

39:07.760 --> 39:09.520
So was it your young boyfriend

39:09.600 --> 39:10.840
who asked you to meet him?

39:19.600 --> 39:20.560
How old is he?

39:23.320 --> 39:24.880
He's graduating from university soon.

39:28.760 --> 39:29.880
How old did you say he was?

39:32.160 --> 39:33.200
Twenty-something.

39:39.360 --> 39:40.760
Where did he tell you to meet him?

39:41.640 --> 39:44.080
In Yihe.

39:52.200 --> 39:53.400
Sang Zhi.

39:53.960 --> 39:54.960
Tell me.

39:56.320 --> 39:57.360
Does your old boyfriend

39:57.960 --> 39:59.440
know how old you are?

40:12.760 --> 40:14.000
What's his phone number?

40:17.880 --> 40:19.200
Are you covering up for him?

40:24.160 --> 40:25.280
Sang Zhi.

40:25.840 --> 40:27.520
I don't want to lose my temper with you,

40:28.040 --> 40:29.240
but you need to know that

40:29.320 --> 40:31.160
your family has
your best interests at heart.

40:31.840 --> 40:33.040
They won't let you date online

40:33.120 --> 40:35.200
because they believe it will harm you.

40:35.760 --> 40:37.000
You can't be in a relationship

40:37.080 --> 40:39.240
until you graduate from high school
and become an adult.

40:40.200 --> 40:42.000
Once you're in college,

40:42.080 --> 40:43.280
you can do whatever you want.

40:43.360 --> 40:44.760
No one will stop you.

40:45.600 --> 40:46.480
Do you hear me?

40:53.440 --> 40:55.280
But I can't resist the temptation.

42:44.160 --> 42:47.000
SLEEPY
